WEBVTT

00:00:30.920 --> 00:00:31.960
Twenty-one days.

00:00:36.520 --> 00:00:37.000
Great.

00:00:38.600 --> 00:00:41.719
Twenty-one days. There are actually twenty-one days left.

00:00:41.920 --> 00:00:43.039
I thought today was...

00:00:43.039 --> 00:00:44.479
But it turns out there are twenty-one days left.

00:00:46.119 --> 00:00:47.439
Are you done yet? Stop acting for me. Turn around.

00:00:48.799 --> 00:00:50.280
Am I dying today or what?

00:00:50.280 --> 00:00:50.920
Twenty-one days.

00:00:51.119 --> 00:00:51.759
Condition is good.

00:00:52.240 --> 00:00:52.719
Not bad.

00:00:53.920 --> 00:00:54.280
No.

00:00:54.560 --> 00:00:55.920
It's not that serious. It's really not.

00:00:56.520 --> 00:00:57.560
Just choked on some smoke.

00:00:57.799 --> 00:00:58.600
Just get some rest.

00:01:00.000 --> 00:01:00.479
Doctor.

00:01:01.439 --> 00:01:02.240
His arm is scratched.

00:01:02.280 --> 00:01:03.880
Should we give him a tetanus shot?

00:01:04.159 --> 00:01:04.959
Let me write an order.

00:01:04.959 --> 00:01:05.280
Okay.

00:01:05.519 --> 00:01:06.079
Xurui.

00:01:06.280 --> 00:01:07.519
No need. It's unnecessary.

00:01:22.920 --> 00:01:23.319
Let's go.

00:01:31.000 --> 00:01:32.400
The three of them probably can't handle my mom.

00:01:33.400 --> 00:01:34.359
Go check for me.

00:01:41.719 --> 00:01:42.519
Xiaocan.

00:01:42.560 --> 00:01:43.000
Go on.

00:02:26.199 --> 00:02:27.639
Guifang, don't worry.

00:02:28.080 --> 00:02:28.960
There must be a way.

00:02:29.840 --> 00:02:30.639
I'm not worried.

00:02:33.000 --> 00:02:35.240
Fang'er, don't listen to those aliens' nonsense.

00:02:35.400 --> 00:02:36.000
That bunch of bastards.

00:02:36.000 --> 00:02:37.159
Can't even figure out their own lives,

00:02:37.280 --> 00:02:38.639
yet they come here acting like prophets.

00:02:38.879 --> 00:02:39.360
Right, right, right.

00:02:40.039 --> 00:02:41.039
Xiao Yin, I just remembered.

00:02:41.560 --> 00:02:43.400
Their calculation formulas are actually quite reasonable.

00:02:43.560 --> 00:02:45.120
Next time we calculate crop yields,

00:02:45.120 --> 00:02:45.680
let's use that.

00:02:55.080 --> 00:02:55.560
Godmother.

00:02:58.680 --> 00:02:59.479
Are you okay?

00:03:01.159 --> 00:03:01.840
I'm fine.

00:03:04.280 --> 00:03:05.680
Haven't we known about this for a while?

00:03:07.400 --> 00:03:09.159
Xurui knew more than two years before I did.

00:03:10.759 --> 00:03:12.599
We should all be mentally prepared.

00:03:13.439 --> 00:03:14.080
Right, Xurui?

00:03:21.400 --> 00:03:22.159
Why are you crying?

00:03:23.199 --> 00:03:24.360
Don't cry. Don't cry.

00:03:27.680 --> 00:03:28.520
It's mealtime, isn't it?

00:03:29.199 --> 00:03:30.159
Let's go. Let's eat at the cafeteria.

00:03:30.919 --> 00:03:31.680
Let's go, let's go.

00:03:32.039 --> 00:03:33.039
Xiao Yin, Li Wai, keep up.

00:03:55.199 --> 00:03:55.879
Just wait.

00:03:56.280 --> 00:03:57.240
Bro got rich overnight.

00:03:57.800 --> 00:03:58.240
I'll take care of you.

00:03:58.680 --> 00:03:59.599
Are you a pig?

00:03:59.840 --> 00:04:00.800
Isn't this your idol?

00:04:00.800 --> 00:04:01.639
Can't you learn from him?

00:04:01.639 --> 00:04:02.120
Have some depth.

00:04:02.120 --> 00:04:03.000
What are you doing here?

00:04:03.000 --> 00:04:03.879
Thinking about life.

00:04:23.279 --> 00:04:25.360
Mom, I'm also proud of you.

00:04:48.199 --> 00:04:50.319
Giving you a chance to be a good person.

00:04:50.959 --> 00:04:52.240
I mean,

00:04:53.199 --> 00:04:54.720
we should just cherish the present.

00:05:00.680 --> 00:05:01.240
Xiaocan.

00:05:01.759 --> 00:05:02.399
Hurry, take a picture of me.

00:05:02.800 --> 00:05:04.040
Lin Xurui.

00:05:21.600 --> 00:05:24.079
Happy New Year.

00:05:54.360 --> 00:05:55.319
Bro, where are you?

00:05:55.399 --> 00:05:56.560
Why aren't you at the campus hospital?

00:05:56.639 --> 00:05:57.120
Xiaocan Bro.

00:05:57.439 --> 00:05:58.319
We're waiting for you at the cafeteria.

00:06:06.800 --> 00:06:07.199
Hello?

00:06:08.040 --> 00:06:08.920
Is my mom okay?

00:06:13.360 --> 00:06:14.519
Come on, come on. Let's eat.

00:06:15.000 --> 00:06:16.079
Why are you staring? Eat.

00:06:17.000 --> 00:06:17.439
Xurui, sit down.

00:06:18.920 --> 00:06:19.639
Eat.

00:06:19.759 --> 00:06:20.759
You must be starving.

00:06:22.160 --> 00:06:22.839
Xiao Yin, have this.

00:06:26.120 --> 00:06:26.560
Xiaocan.

00:06:29.519 --> 00:06:31.120
Why are you all standing? Sit.

00:06:31.879 --> 00:06:32.959
Starving for half the day. Eat up, quick.

00:07:11.120 --> 00:07:12.279
Why did you sit down yourself?

00:07:14.879 --> 00:07:15.720
Go get the food.

00:07:16.720 --> 00:07:17.839
Expecting me to serve you?

00:07:24.759 --> 00:07:25.240
What's wrong?

00:07:27.759 --> 00:07:28.720
Don't know what to eat?

00:07:30.439 --> 00:07:31.879
Aren't you full of big ideas?

00:07:33.680 --> 00:07:35.079
Daring to make any decision yourself.

00:07:37.000 --> 00:07:38.360
Without consulting your mom about anything.

00:07:49.720 --> 00:07:50.079
Mom.

00:07:51.680 --> 00:07:52.480
Calm down.

00:07:53.800 --> 00:07:54.279
If you want to scold me...

00:07:54.279 --> 00:07:55.560
How much is left on your meal card?

00:07:57.720 --> 00:07:59.519
Go buy Xurui something she likes to eat.

00:08:02.279 --> 00:08:03.600
And buy me a bottle of Coke.

00:08:06.000 --> 00:08:07.279
You do the math.

00:08:08.040 --> 00:08:09.319
Don't be gone next month

00:08:09.439 --> 00:08:10.319
with money still on the card.

00:08:15.639 --> 00:08:16.519
Godmother.

00:08:17.439 --> 00:08:18.639
What are you doing?

00:09:04.799 --> 00:09:05.120
Hello?

00:09:05.960 --> 00:09:06.840
Still haven't found her.

00:09:06.919 --> 00:09:07.519
Keep looking.

00:09:07.759 --> 00:09:09.080
I'll go home and see if my mom went back.

00:09:09.200 --> 00:09:10.480
How could she disappear in just a moment?

00:09:12.679 --> 00:09:13.679
Godmother went to the restroom just now.

00:09:14.240 --> 00:09:15.320
Why didn't you go in with her?

00:09:15.840 --> 00:09:16.919
I didn't... why would I go in?

00:09:17.039 --> 00:09:17.720
How was I supposed to know Guifang...

00:09:17.720 --> 00:09:18.519
...would get lost just going to the restroom?

00:09:18.519 --> 00:09:19.759
If you knew, why didn't you go in?

00:09:21.720 --> 00:09:22.919
My fault, my fault.

00:09:23.720 --> 00:09:24.399
I'm sorry, I'm sorry.

00:09:24.559 --> 00:09:25.039
I...

00:09:25.159 --> 00:09:26.720
I sh... I should have followed Godmother in.

00:09:26.919 --> 00:09:27.559
I just didn't think of it just now.

00:09:27.559 --> 00:09:28.159
Now you say it.

00:09:28.519 --> 00:09:29.039
Xiao Yin.

00:09:29.399 --> 00:09:29.840
Xiao Yin.

00:09:32.039 --> 00:09:32.480
Take it slow.

00:09:35.120 --> 00:09:35.399
There.

00:09:36.279 --> 00:09:37.480
Ma Jianfei, A Fu.

00:09:38.799 --> 00:09:39.279
Run! Run!

00:09:39.720 --> 00:09:41.200
You two stand right there! Don't run!

00:09:41.519 --> 00:09:42.720
I won't accept that my son...

00:09:42.720 --> 00:09:44.039
...has only twenty-one days left to live.

00:09:45.879 --> 00:09:46.720
Open it for me.

00:09:47.440 --> 00:09:48.159
Open it!

00:09:52.120 --> 00:09:52.639
Run!

00:09:53.720 --> 00:09:54.360
Stand still! Don't run!

00:09:54.360 --> 00:09:55.159
Wait, wait, wait! Hold on!

00:09:55.279 --> 00:09:56.679
The pact Kong Xiaocan signed with me...

00:09:56.679 --> 00:09:57.399
...is written in black and white.

00:09:57.399 --> 00:09:58.360
You can't change it.

00:10:01.919 --> 00:10:03.399
Extend Xiaocan's life for me.

00:10:03.840 --> 00:10:04.559
Or else I will...

00:10:04.559 --> 00:10:05.360
I have a way!

00:10:05.360 --> 00:10:06.320
I have a way!

00:10:07.519 --> 00:10:08.159
I have a way!

00:10:08.399 --> 00:10:10.639
I can make you a temporary Lifespan Agent.

00:10:10.799 --> 00:10:11.960
To extend your son's life.

00:10:12.480 --> 00:10:13.120
Are you serious?

00:10:13.639 --> 00:10:14.159
Calm down.

00:10:14.759 --> 00:10:15.639
Put my nephew down first.

00:10:16.240 --> 00:10:16.759
Calm down first.

00:10:17.000 --> 00:10:17.360
Put him down.

00:10:17.519 --> 00:10:18.320
Put him down, put him down, put him down.

00:10:18.519 --> 00:10:19.360
We can't run away anyway.

00:10:19.440 --> 00:10:20.720
You've got us cornered.

00:10:21.639 --> 00:10:22.000
Put him down.

00:10:27.320 --> 00:10:28.440
Yes, just like that.

00:10:29.120 --> 00:10:29.879
Take off the watch.

00:10:30.559 --> 00:10:30.879
The watch.

00:10:30.960 --> 00:10:31.480
Will this work?

00:10:31.879 --> 00:10:32.639
What else can we do?

00:10:33.559 --> 00:10:33.919
Really?

00:10:34.600 --> 00:10:35.159
Go get the pact.

00:10:37.399 --> 00:10:38.039
This thing...

00:10:38.600 --> 00:10:41.559
...is an important tool for us to trade life.

00:10:42.440 --> 00:10:43.159
Once you have it...

00:10:43.600 --> 00:10:44.159
...you can...

00:10:44.440 --> 00:10:46.480
...absorb the Life Energy of other living things...

00:10:46.679 --> 00:10:47.639
...and transfer it to Xiaocan.

00:10:49.759 --> 00:10:50.240
How do I do it?

00:10:51.519 --> 00:10:53.879
Look at this pot of sweet potato trying to bloom.

00:10:54.120 --> 00:10:56.919
We make a simple life pact with it.

00:10:57.519 --> 00:10:58.039
Like this.

00:11:05.480 --> 00:11:08.840
Then use this, point at it, and press here.

00:11:09.399 --> 00:11:10.000
Confirm.

00:11:13.799 --> 00:11:14.639
And the trade is complete.

00:11:16.039 --> 00:11:16.600
In this process...

00:11:16.720 --> 00:11:17.440
...this Service Fee...

00:11:17.440 --> 00:11:19.720
...is the necessary cost for energy conversion.

00:11:20.159 --> 00:11:21.440
And this Personal Commission...

00:11:21.559 --> 00:11:23.120
...you can use a third-party pact...

00:11:23.240 --> 00:11:24.639
...to extract the energy for Xiaocan.

00:11:25.799 --> 00:11:27.960
That 11.3 ti...

00:11:28.399 --> 00:11:30.279
...is the count of Life Energy.

00:11:30.440 --> 00:11:32.279
It's roughly equivalent to ten seconds of human life.

00:11:32.639 --> 00:11:34.279
The conversion rate for plants is very low.

00:11:34.440 --> 00:11:35.799
That's why we look for humans.

00:11:40.320 --> 00:11:40.799
I understand.

00:11:43.519 --> 00:11:44.000
Wait a minute.

00:11:44.679 --> 00:11:45.519
Let me remind you of one thing.

00:11:46.000 --> 00:11:47.000
You only have one day.

00:11:47.120 --> 00:11:48.399
It will expire at midnight tonight.

00:11:53.759 --> 00:11:54.120
Nephew.

00:11:55.840 --> 00:11:56.440
Scared me to death.

00:11:57.960 --> 00:11:58.360
Mom.

00:11:58.919 --> 00:11:59.279
Mom.

00:12:00.200 --> 00:12:00.639
Mom.

00:12:11.279 --> 00:12:12.559
We found Auntie. She's at the hospital.

00:12:12.960 --> 00:12:13.840
Xiaocan, come here quick.

00:12:14.639 --> 00:12:15.000
Hurry up.

00:12:15.799 --> 00:12:16.120
Okay.

00:12:19.759 --> 00:12:21.120
It was in this lousy hospital...

00:12:21.120 --> 00:12:22.000
...that Xiaocan was driven to a dead end.

00:12:22.559 --> 00:12:23.200
The number of people here who can trade...

00:12:23.200 --> 00:12:24.519
...must be higher than anywhere else.

00:12:25.080 --> 00:12:26.080
We'll split up in a bit.

00:12:26.120 --> 00:12:26.960
The odds are better that way.

00:12:27.600 --> 00:12:28.919
I suspect the ICU entrance...

00:12:29.200 --> 00:12:31.240
...and the pediatric cancer ward are the most likely.

00:12:31.639 --> 00:12:33.320
There must be plenty of parents willing to trade for their kids.

00:12:33.879 --> 00:12:35.080
And fools like Xiaocan...

00:12:35.360 --> 00:12:36.279
...who are willing to trade for their parents.

00:12:36.679 --> 00:12:37.559
We'll take a commission on those.

00:12:38.000 --> 00:12:38.720
If we can find someone...

00:12:39.000 --> 00:12:40.320
...willing to swap lives directly with Xiaocan...

00:12:40.320 --> 00:12:41.279
...that would be perfect.

00:12:41.440 --> 00:12:42.320
Let's split up.

00:12:42.519 --> 00:12:42.919
Let's go.

00:12:43.200 --> 00:12:43.879
I'll go wait for Xiaocan.

00:12:47.519 --> 00:12:48.080
Let's go!

00:12:49.240 --> 00:12:50.879
We only have tonight left.

00:12:51.600 --> 00:12:52.000
Guifang.

00:12:52.840 --> 00:12:53.879
Why don't you use mine first?

00:12:55.200 --> 00:12:56.120
Why would I use yours?

00:12:58.799 --> 00:12:59.799
I don't want yours.

00:13:00.240 --> 00:13:01.559
I want you to find people who can trade.

00:13:01.919 --> 00:13:02.399
But...

00:13:03.120 --> 00:13:04.440
When I was livestreaming sales...

00:13:04.960 --> 00:13:06.200
...if I knew a product's formula was bad...

00:13:06.200 --> 00:13:07.080
...I couldn't bring myself to say it.

00:13:07.559 --> 00:13:08.360
That Osmanthus Yogurt...

00:13:08.720 --> 00:13:09.720
...would at most give people diarrhea.

00:13:10.200 --> 00:13:11.080
Now we're taking people's lives.

00:13:12.320 --> 00:13:13.440
We absolutely cannot do this.

00:13:13.559 --> 00:13:14.480
Don't talk to me about your...

00:13:14.480 --> 00:13:15.519
...Osmanthus Yogurt business!

00:13:16.000 --> 00:13:17.120
Why can't you just say it?

00:13:17.639 --> 00:13:19.000
Just tell people who you are.

00:13:19.240 --> 00:13:20.159
Sign a few autographs for them.

00:13:20.159 --> 00:13:21.200
You could get a month or two in exchange.

00:13:21.720 --> 00:13:23.200
My autograph takes someone's life?

00:13:23.840 --> 00:13:24.639
How is that okay?

00:13:24.720 --> 00:13:25.759
Why not do it for a brother?

00:13:26.360 --> 00:13:27.759
Why not do it for my Godmother?

00:13:27.879 --> 00:13:28.480
Exactly.

00:13:29.039 --> 00:13:30.000
Can you really just stand by...

00:13:30.000 --> 00:13:31.279
...and watch Guifang give up on Xiaocan?

00:13:31.559 --> 00:13:33.279
What mother would give up on her own son?

00:13:33.759 --> 00:13:34.080
Xurui.

00:13:34.440 --> 00:13:34.840
Let's go.

00:13:35.360 --> 00:13:36.039
Xiao Yin.

00:13:40.120 --> 00:13:40.600
Auntie.

00:13:42.320 --> 00:13:43.360
We can't do this.

00:13:48.399 --> 00:13:49.120
Xurui.

00:13:51.120 --> 00:13:53.440
You're the closest person to Xiaocan besides me.

00:13:54.480 --> 00:13:55.480
Don't you want to save him?

00:14:26.679 --> 00:14:27.960
Bro, I'm waiting for you at the door

00:14:27.960 --> 00:14:28.559
Hurry up

00:14:30.399 --> 00:14:31.039
Bro, Bro, over here

00:14:31.279 --> 00:14:31.879
You're finally here

00:14:32.159 --> 00:14:32.639
Let me tell you

00:14:32.919 --> 00:14:34.200
There are many in Pediatrics willing to exchange

00:14:34.279 --> 00:14:35.919
But they only want to exchange for their own children

00:14:36.039 --> 00:14:37.000
Godmother is chatting with them right now

00:14:37.279 --> 00:14:38.120
I calculated it for you

00:14:38.120 --> 00:14:39.080
Even if we only charge the agency fee

00:14:39.120 --> 00:14:40.440
you can live until your child grows up

00:14:40.679 --> 00:14:41.879
Bro, you're saved

00:14:42.080 --> 00:14:43.440
Quick, quick, come with me, quick

00:14:47.519 --> 00:14:48.759
I'm sending the contract to you now

00:14:50.639 --> 00:14:51.720
I need to make this clear to you

00:14:52.039 --> 00:14:53.039
If you exchange twenty years

00:14:53.240 --> 00:14:54.600
the child will only get ten years

00:14:55.080 --> 00:14:56.840
I can't change this rule either

00:14:57.360 --> 00:14:58.960
So you must think it through clearly

00:14:59.279 --> 00:15:01.080
It's good for the child to live ten more years

00:15:01.240 --> 00:15:02.840
We'll exchange as much as we can

00:15:03.120 --> 00:15:03.399
Right

00:15:04.000 --> 00:15:05.639
Everything is worth it for the child

00:15:05.759 --> 00:15:06.840
Is there a quota limit

00:15:06.960 --> 00:15:07.879
Can we cut in line

00:15:08.000 --> 00:15:08.840
There is no quota limit

00:15:09.039 --> 00:15:10.440
If you have friends who want to exchange too

00:15:10.440 --> 00:15:11.399
call them all over

00:15:11.519 --> 00:15:12.440
The more people, the better

00:15:12.559 --> 00:15:13.440
So when can we exchange

00:15:13.720 --> 00:15:15.279
Our child really can't wait any longer

00:15:15.440 --> 00:15:16.759
Very soon, we can exchange very soon

00:15:17.080 --> 00:15:18.200
Finish reading the contract and sign it

00:15:18.200 --> 00:15:19.080
We can exchange immediately

00:15:19.559 --> 00:15:20.679
If you don't believe me

00:15:20.799 --> 00:15:21.879
I can use two of your days

00:15:22.120 --> 00:15:23.039
to exchange for one day for the child

00:15:23.840 --> 00:15:24.600
She just exchanged some

00:15:24.799 --> 00:15:25.559
Tell them

00:15:25.600 --> 00:15:27.600
Yes, I just used two days to get one day

00:15:27.799 --> 00:15:28.720
It really works

00:15:29.039 --> 00:15:30.759
The child's condition was deteriorating rapidly

00:15:30.840 --> 00:15:32.480
Now all indicators are normal

00:15:32.559 --> 00:15:32.919
Yes

00:15:33.200 --> 00:15:34.039
I didn't lie to you, right

00:15:34.440 --> 00:15:35.039
Look, quickly

00:15:35.120 --> 00:15:35.639
Come, Xiao Yin

00:15:36.960 --> 00:15:38.360
Godmother, Xiaocan is here

00:15:38.960 --> 00:15:39.399
Xiaocan

00:15:39.679 --> 00:15:40.480
Xiaocan, come in quickly

00:15:41.519 --> 00:15:42.639
Mom has settled it with them

00:15:42.679 --> 00:15:43.960
You all agreed and can sign, right

00:15:44.039 --> 00:15:45.320
Sign, sign, sign

00:15:45.519 --> 00:15:46.799
Mom found a way to save you

00:15:47.159 --> 00:15:47.960
Quick, Xiao Yin

00:15:48.200 --> 00:15:50.159
So you're going to leave them without parents now

00:15:50.879 --> 00:15:51.720
Those ten years

00:15:52.159 --> 00:15:53.039
After fifteen years

00:15:53.039 --> 00:15:54.639
they will still leave, right

00:15:56.000 --> 00:15:56.799
Leaving now

00:15:57.279 --> 00:15:58.320
is within their parents' love

00:15:59.399 --> 00:16:00.039
But what about later

00:16:00.879 --> 00:16:01.480
What about next time

00:16:02.480 --> 00:16:03.639
There is no later, no next time

00:16:03.639 --> 00:16:04.360
I want it now

00:16:04.559 --> 00:16:05.720
I want to save my son now

00:16:05.960 --> 00:16:06.279
Quick

00:16:06.480 --> 00:16:07.159
Xiaocan, sign quickly

00:16:07.960 --> 00:16:08.440
Just press here

00:16:11.919 --> 00:16:12.360
Kong Xiaocan

00:16:12.879 --> 00:16:13.600
Kong Xiaocan, where are you going

00:16:13.600 --> 00:16:13.960
Xiaocan

00:16:13.960 --> 00:16:14.360
Kong Xiaocan

00:16:14.360 --> 00:16:14.679
Xiaocan

00:16:14.679 --> 00:16:15.440
Kong Xiaocan, where are you going

00:16:16.519 --> 00:16:17.279
Wei Mingtian, move aside

00:16:17.679 --> 00:16:18.759
Wei Mingtian, are you crazy

00:16:32.440 --> 00:16:32.840
Xiaocan

00:16:33.960 --> 00:16:34.639
Are you okay

00:16:44.080 --> 00:16:45.120
What you just said

00:16:46.559 --> 00:16:47.720
made me realize something

00:16:49.720 --> 00:16:51.159
I always thought I was very brave

00:16:52.879 --> 00:16:53.919
But now I realize

00:16:55.080 --> 00:16:56.720
I might be the one who isn't brave

00:17:07.039 --> 00:17:07.799
How could that be?

00:17:09.200 --> 00:17:10.359
You gave your life

00:17:11.079 --> 00:17:12.079
to your mother.

00:17:13.039 --> 00:17:13.880
What else

00:17:14.759 --> 00:17:15.920
could be braver than that?

00:17:17.640 --> 00:17:18.279
It wasn't brave.

00:17:20.119 --> 00:17:20.920
It was cowardly.

00:17:22.039 --> 00:17:22.799
It was escapism.

00:17:26.200 --> 00:17:27.240
Think about it. Back then,

00:17:27.880 --> 00:17:29.039
when I signed the pact with A Fu,

00:17:30.200 --> 00:17:31.319
I was pretty smug at first.

00:17:32.519 --> 00:17:34.279
I thought I was the most filial son in the world.

00:17:35.880 --> 00:17:37.279
But then I slowly realized

00:17:38.519 --> 00:17:39.440
that actually,

00:17:40.880 --> 00:17:41.920
it was also because I didn't have the guts

00:17:41.920 --> 00:17:43.319
to face the fact that I wouldn't have a mom.

00:17:45.880 --> 00:17:48.240
When I realized that in exchange for those 50 years,

00:17:48.960 --> 00:17:50.799
I could leave this world at any moment,

00:17:52.240 --> 00:17:52.880
I was scared.

00:17:53.960 --> 00:17:54.480
Anxious.

00:17:56.839 --> 00:17:57.640
And guilty.

00:17:59.319 --> 00:18:01.000
If I'm the one who leaves first,

00:18:02.799 --> 00:18:04.839
I won't have to endure the pain of losing a loved one.

00:18:08.559 --> 00:18:09.599
But I didn't realize

00:18:11.000 --> 00:18:12.240
that by doing so,

00:18:13.000 --> 00:18:14.599
I was also passing the pain on to my mom.

00:18:16.599 --> 00:18:17.279
And you.

00:18:24.359 --> 00:18:25.799
Whether it's parents losing their child

00:18:27.319 --> 00:18:28.519
or a child losing their parents,

00:18:29.279 --> 00:18:30.200
it's all too painful.

00:18:33.240 --> 00:18:34.799
That's why I can't accept that Life Energy.

00:18:36.160 --> 00:18:38.000
It's too cruel to each of their families.

00:18:38.839 --> 00:18:39.720
I can't do it.

00:18:43.160 --> 00:18:44.400
But in this situation,

00:18:45.400 --> 00:18:46.119
for Auntie,

00:18:47.000 --> 00:18:47.799
it's also cruel.

00:18:52.519 --> 00:18:53.799
Is there really no solution?

00:18:55.400 --> 00:18:57.160
But none of us did anything wrong.

00:18:59.079 --> 00:19:00.039
No, I'm the one who was wrong.

00:19:02.000 --> 00:19:03.160
I shouldn't have made the decision for my mom.

00:19:06.079 --> 00:19:07.240
But this is how things are now.

00:19:15.720 --> 00:19:16.640
That decision you made back then,

00:19:18.119 --> 00:19:19.319
you don't regret it at all,

00:19:19.839 --> 00:19:20.240
do you?

00:19:23.440 --> 00:19:24.039
I don't regret it.

00:19:26.759 --> 00:19:28.680
And I will bear the consequences I have to bear.

00:19:35.920 --> 00:19:36.279
Okay.

00:19:37.960 --> 00:19:38.680
Then I support you.

00:19:46.079 --> 00:19:47.799
Why is your face so dirty?

00:19:50.000 --> 00:19:50.920
It won't even wipe off.

00:19:52.200 --> 00:19:53.920
Look how filthy it is. Here.

00:20:04.400 --> 00:20:04.839
Xiaocan

00:20:05.559 --> 00:20:06.799
Godmother, Xiaocan is here.

00:20:07.079 --> 00:20:07.480
Quick.

00:20:12.759 --> 00:20:13.200
Mom.

00:20:14.240 --> 00:20:15.559
Kong Xiaocan, why are you running?

00:20:16.599 --> 00:20:17.200
Mom, I was wrong.

00:20:18.480 --> 00:20:19.960
I shouldn't have transferred fifty years of energy

00:20:20.200 --> 00:20:20.960
to you in secret.

00:20:21.920 --> 00:20:22.680
I really know I was wrong.

00:20:24.319 --> 00:20:25.039
Sign this right now.

00:20:25.279 --> 00:20:26.480
Sign all of these for me right now.

00:20:26.559 --> 00:20:27.319
Hurry up.

00:20:27.440 --> 00:20:27.960
Be quick.

00:20:28.279 --> 00:20:28.799
Sign it.

00:20:29.160 --> 00:20:29.960
Mom, Mom.

00:20:30.799 --> 00:20:31.200
Mom.

00:20:31.440 --> 00:20:32.400
Sign it quickly.

00:20:32.400 --> 00:20:33.599
If my trading energy to you was wrong,

00:20:33.599 --> 00:20:34.960
isn't what you're doing now also wrong?

00:20:35.119 --> 00:20:36.640
We can't keep making mistakes, okay?

00:20:36.920 --> 00:20:37.880
We can't bring ourselves to do it, right?

00:20:37.880 --> 00:20:39.400
Even if I can't, I have to.

00:20:40.000 --> 00:20:40.920
Kong Guifang.

00:20:44.799 --> 00:20:46.039
Look at what you've become.

00:20:48.480 --> 00:20:49.519
I've never seen you

00:20:49.519 --> 00:20:50.279
be like this in my whole life.

00:20:51.799 --> 00:20:52.319
Fine.

00:20:52.839 --> 00:20:53.400
If I sign,

00:20:54.119 --> 00:20:54.680
what happens next?

00:20:55.079 --> 00:20:56.440
If our tomatoes at home go bad,

00:20:56.759 --> 00:20:57.839
or the lab seeds have issues,

00:20:57.839 --> 00:20:58.480
do we have to trade for them all?

00:20:58.480 --> 00:20:59.359
Why would I trade for those?

00:20:59.359 --> 00:21:00.319
Are those my son?

00:21:00.319 --> 00:21:01.559
Anyway, this whole thing is wrong.

00:21:01.720 --> 00:21:02.759
Kong Xiaocan, are you out of your mind?

00:21:03.039 --> 00:21:04.119
Isn't your mom doing this for you?

00:21:04.240 --> 00:21:04.720
Kong Xiaocan.

00:21:05.440 --> 00:21:06.440
Do you think we can just stand by

00:21:06.440 --> 00:21:07.359
and watch you die?

00:21:07.440 --> 00:21:08.519
But have you ever thought about it?

00:21:09.079 --> 00:21:09.599
Trading back and forth,

00:21:09.759 --> 00:21:10.839
all the Life Energy goes to the aliens.

00:21:11.079 --> 00:21:12.119
Isn't that wasting life?

00:21:12.599 --> 00:21:14.240
Wei Mingtian, your logic is sound.

00:21:14.480 --> 00:21:15.519
But Xiaocan is my brother.

00:21:15.799 --> 00:21:17.119
When it comes to my brother,

00:21:17.200 --> 00:21:18.359
there's no logic to discuss.

00:21:18.359 --> 00:21:19.640
But even if Xiaocan survives,

00:21:20.440 --> 00:21:21.480
do you think he'll be happy?

00:21:21.480 --> 00:21:22.759
Then do you think I will be happy?

00:21:23.240 --> 00:21:24.079
If I'm the only one left,

00:21:24.079 --> 00:21:24.880
can I live well?

00:21:24.880 --> 00:21:25.960
Can I live happily?

00:21:26.119 --> 00:21:26.960
Why can't you?

00:21:29.000 --> 00:21:29.319
Mom.

00:21:30.559 --> 00:21:31.200
Think about it.

00:21:32.160 --> 00:21:33.680
Have you ever really lived for yourself?

00:21:35.480 --> 00:21:37.000
Now that you finally have this chance,

00:21:37.839 --> 00:21:39.440
why can't you live for yourself for once?

00:21:44.480 --> 00:21:45.359
That's impossible.

00:21:54.680 --> 00:21:56.279
Are you done arguing?

00:21:56.720 --> 00:21:59.079
The whole hospital can hear you fighting.

00:21:59.359 --> 00:22:01.519
My grandpa says he wants to exchange Life Energy with you.

00:22:02.480 --> 00:22:03.359
Sorry, little girl.

00:22:04.119 --> 00:22:04.880
There's no such thing.

00:22:05.599 --> 00:22:06.240
Who says there isn't?

00:22:07.279 --> 00:22:07.920
Where is your grandpa?

00:22:11.200 --> 00:22:12.079
Grandpa.

00:22:13.240 --> 00:22:14.720
I brought them back.

00:22:17.799 --> 00:22:18.599
Hello.

00:22:21.319 --> 00:22:22.480
Give me a few minutes.

00:22:23.920 --> 00:22:24.799
This painkiller...

00:22:24.799 --> 00:22:26.240
It'll kick in in a moment.

00:22:27.720 --> 00:22:28.640
I have experience with it.

00:22:29.559 --> 00:22:31.480
The time this medicine works is getting shorter.

00:22:32.319 --> 00:22:34.400
Now it lasts half an hour at most.

00:22:38.480 --> 00:22:39.359
Kong Xiaocan.

00:22:40.359 --> 00:22:41.200
Yes, it's me.

00:22:41.720 --> 00:22:43.880
You saved your mother from this kind of suffering.

00:22:44.680 --> 00:22:45.680
That's really wonderful.

00:22:51.880 --> 00:22:52.279
You...

00:22:53.000 --> 00:22:54.279
You know my name?

00:22:55.680 --> 00:22:57.839
I heard you are all from Duxing University.

00:22:58.759 --> 00:23:00.640
Which departments are you in?

00:23:01.480 --> 00:23:02.759
We have some from the Department of Agriculture.

00:23:03.160 --> 00:23:04.119
Some from Water Conservancy.

00:23:04.400 --> 00:23:05.559
I'm in Library Science.

00:23:06.119 --> 00:23:07.240
I'm a recommended grad student.

00:23:08.799 --> 00:23:09.559
What a coincidence.

00:23:10.359 --> 00:23:10.839
It turns out...

00:23:11.799 --> 00:23:13.440
I used to teach Library Science.

00:23:15.240 --> 00:23:16.680
But I retired a long time ago.

00:23:17.200 --> 00:23:18.480
I didn't get the chance to teach you.

00:23:21.400 --> 00:23:22.440
Enough small talk.

00:23:23.799 --> 00:23:24.680
Kong Guifang.

00:23:25.720 --> 00:23:26.400
Just now...

00:23:27.000 --> 00:23:29.000
You were so fierce when you came in.

00:23:30.160 --> 00:23:31.000
But now...

00:23:31.640 --> 00:23:32.759
Don't be reserved.

00:23:34.039 --> 00:23:34.599
Let's see...

00:23:35.319 --> 00:23:36.440
How much I can give the child

00:23:36.839 --> 00:23:37.759
in exchange.

00:23:39.680 --> 00:23:40.559
I'll exchange it to him.

00:23:47.119 --> 00:23:47.680
What's wrong?

00:23:52.519 --> 00:23:54.240
You are a professor at Duxing University.

00:23:55.759 --> 00:23:56.880
You're our teacher.

00:23:58.359 --> 00:23:59.240
I can't trade with you.

00:24:01.960 --> 00:24:03.200
Trading with strangers...

00:24:04.519 --> 00:24:05.799
carries no guilt.

00:24:08.000 --> 00:24:09.079
But hearing there's a connection...

00:24:09.839 --> 00:24:11.000
I just can't do it.

00:24:16.200 --> 00:24:16.960
You guys...

00:24:17.960 --> 00:24:18.839
Trading with me...

00:24:20.319 --> 00:24:21.960
also makes my life...

00:24:22.519 --> 00:24:23.480
more meaningful.

00:24:25.240 --> 00:24:26.920
But where there's life, there's hope.

00:24:29.759 --> 00:24:30.799
My ears...

00:24:31.079 --> 00:24:32.000
work just fine.

00:24:33.200 --> 00:24:33.920
A person...

00:24:34.720 --> 00:24:36.160
as long as they've lived well...

00:24:36.880 --> 00:24:38.200
won't die in vain.

00:24:40.240 --> 00:24:41.039
In my life...

00:24:42.079 --> 00:24:43.279
I have many regrets.

00:24:44.279 --> 00:24:45.200
When I was young...

00:24:45.759 --> 00:24:47.039
the war hadn't ended yet...

00:24:47.559 --> 00:24:49.400
and my mother passed away.

00:24:50.799 --> 00:24:51.640
Later on...

00:24:52.400 --> 00:24:53.839
whether it was my studies...

00:24:53.839 --> 00:24:55.160
or my career...

00:24:55.799 --> 00:24:57.079
there were ups and downs.

00:24:58.599 --> 00:24:59.920
But thinking about it now...

00:25:01.240 --> 00:25:02.480
for the majority of that time...

00:25:04.119 --> 00:25:05.640
I lived well.

00:25:06.880 --> 00:25:08.680
So let's not spend these last days...

00:25:09.559 --> 00:25:10.319
living miserably.

00:25:13.319 --> 00:25:14.400
You look like the kind of person...

00:25:14.920 --> 00:25:15.960
who dedicated their life to knowledge...

00:25:16.640 --> 00:25:18.599
and made great academic contributions.

00:25:19.000 --> 00:25:20.319
Naturally, compared to most of us...

00:25:20.480 --> 00:25:21.680
you've lived a better, more brilliant life.

00:25:22.359 --> 00:25:24.079
Who says living well...

00:25:25.240 --> 00:25:27.160
means studying every day?

00:25:27.720 --> 00:25:28.960
Pursuing knowledge...

00:25:29.279 --> 00:25:30.799
is certainly joyful.

00:25:31.160 --> 00:25:32.960
But when I was young...

00:25:33.599 --> 00:25:34.359
playing soccer...

00:25:35.119 --> 00:25:35.880
playing cards...

00:25:36.680 --> 00:25:39.079
traveling with classmates...

00:25:40.279 --> 00:25:41.039
and falling in love...

00:25:42.359 --> 00:25:43.759
were all very happy times too.

00:25:45.480 --> 00:25:46.480
When I got old...

00:25:46.960 --> 00:25:47.960
besides compiling textbooks...

00:25:48.119 --> 00:25:49.160
and writing papers...

00:25:50.400 --> 00:25:51.920
I also spent time with my family...

00:25:53.279 --> 00:25:54.480
and my little granddaughter.

00:25:55.279 --> 00:25:56.400
We chatted...

00:25:57.559 --> 00:25:58.279
had picnics...

00:25:58.839 --> 00:25:59.799
and went to amusement parks.

00:26:00.519 --> 00:26:01.920
I taught her to play video games...

00:26:02.960 --> 00:26:04.319
and she taught me to catch dolls.

00:26:07.880 --> 00:26:10.200
That's living well every single day.

00:26:17.319 --> 00:26:17.720
Yes.

00:26:21.480 --> 00:26:22.359
Amusement parks...

00:26:23.400 --> 00:26:24.359
are really fun.

00:26:29.440 --> 00:26:30.519
My dad...

00:26:31.960 --> 00:26:33.559
has always respected our thoughts.

00:26:34.799 --> 00:26:35.599
And now...

00:26:35.920 --> 00:26:37.039
we respect his thoughts too.

00:26:37.640 --> 00:26:38.839
But Grandpa...

00:26:39.480 --> 00:26:40.960
you have to remember me forever.

00:26:42.599 --> 00:26:44.920
Grandpa will remember you forever.

00:26:45.799 --> 00:26:47.519
You must remember Grandpa too.

00:26:48.880 --> 00:26:49.960
Remember...

00:26:50.960 --> 00:26:51.720
Grandpa...

00:26:52.720 --> 00:26:54.400
loves you forever.

00:26:55.039 --> 00:26:55.480
Come here.

00:26:55.960 --> 00:26:56.440
Okay.

00:26:56.759 --> 00:26:57.680
Let's pinky swear.

00:26:58.000 --> 00:27:02.880
Pinky swear, for a hundred years, no changing.

00:27:20.279 --> 00:27:20.720
Alright.

00:27:22.119 --> 00:27:23.359
I need to see my guests out now.

00:27:24.519 --> 00:27:25.720
The remaining time...

00:27:27.480 --> 00:27:29.039
is for my family.

00:28:50.079 --> 00:28:50.559
Godmother...

00:28:51.680 --> 00:28:52.279
are we...

00:28:53.400 --> 00:28:54.240
still continuing?

00:29:06.359 --> 00:29:06.960
I'm done.

00:29:09.400 --> 00:29:10.880
However many days Xiaocan has left...

00:29:11.839 --> 00:29:13.240
let him just live them well.

00:29:15.240 --> 00:29:16.440
I'll go to the pediatrics ward later...

00:29:17.400 --> 00:29:18.440
and apologize to the parents.

00:29:19.960 --> 00:29:20.640
I'll go, Mom.

00:29:21.640 --> 00:29:23.240
I caused this whole thing anyway.

00:29:29.880 --> 00:29:30.440
Xiaocan...

00:29:32.359 --> 00:29:33.559
have you really thought this through?

00:29:36.079 --> 00:29:38.000
Do you really feel you've lived well?

00:29:41.400 --> 00:29:41.799
Mom...

00:29:43.240 --> 00:29:44.680
living with you these twenty-odd years...

00:29:46.400 --> 00:29:48.240
and the time spent with everyone...

00:29:51.160 --> 00:29:52.440
I feel I've lived very well.

00:30:14.000 --> 00:30:16.880
Little Daxue has a malignant brain tumor.

00:30:17.160 --> 00:30:19.519
But his other organs are healthy.

00:30:20.079 --> 00:30:21.880
For example, his heart, liver,

00:30:22.240 --> 00:30:23.319
corneas, and kidneys.

00:30:23.839 --> 00:30:24.839
They can be used to save

00:30:24.839 --> 00:30:26.519
three to four critically ill children,

00:30:27.119 --> 00:30:29.319
and restore sight to two blind children.

00:30:30.319 --> 00:30:31.720
He is currently brain dead.

00:30:32.599 --> 00:30:34.440
Maintaining life support carries risks.

00:30:34.960 --> 00:30:37.720
We are concerned about sudden multiple organ failure.

00:30:38.160 --> 00:30:39.720
Since he has been sick for quite a while,

00:30:40.079 --> 00:30:40.559
so,

00:30:40.680 --> 00:30:42.640
some drugs in his body haven't fully metabolized.

00:30:43.240 --> 00:30:44.920
We estimate that in seven days,

00:30:45.000 --> 00:30:46.200
the drugs will be completely metabolized.

00:30:46.559 --> 00:30:48.680
Then he can save even more children.

00:30:50.200 --> 00:30:50.960
Please think it over.

00:31:02.000 --> 00:31:02.319
Mom.

00:31:03.920 --> 00:31:05.759
This child needs exactly seven days.

00:31:08.880 --> 00:31:09.559
Let's give it to him.

00:31:24.680 --> 00:31:25.039
Hello.

00:31:25.720 --> 00:31:26.480
We have decided

00:31:27.319 --> 00:31:29.000
to give you these seven days of Life Energy.

00:31:29.359 --> 00:31:31.400
You just need to sign the Pact.

00:31:40.599 --> 00:31:41.279
Kong Xiaocan.

00:31:42.440 --> 00:31:42.960
Thank you.

00:31:44.000 --> 00:31:45.359
Thank you for letting our child

00:31:45.359 --> 00:31:46.400
continue to live on.

00:31:47.079 --> 00:31:47.519
Thank you.

00:31:49.039 --> 00:31:49.519
Live on.

00:31:50.599 --> 00:31:50.960
Yes.

00:31:52.000 --> 00:31:53.200
His heart is still beating.

00:31:54.559 --> 00:31:56.519
His eyes can still see this world.

00:31:57.880 --> 00:31:59.039
He is still with us.

00:33:26.160 --> 00:33:28.039
Is everything with Kong Guifang handled?

00:33:28.519 --> 00:33:29.279
It's all taken care of.

00:33:29.599 --> 00:33:32.079
The memories of unrelated personnel in the hospital have been erased.

00:33:35.079 --> 00:33:35.759
This time,

00:33:36.240 --> 00:33:36.799
there will definitely

00:33:37.160 --> 00:33:37.960
be no problems.

00:33:38.440 --> 00:33:39.160
It's definitely safe now.

00:33:44.559 --> 00:33:45.079
Boss.

00:33:46.119 --> 00:33:47.200
Sometimes I think humans

00:33:48.200 --> 00:33:48.960
are quite interesting.

00:33:50.759 --> 00:33:51.440
How so?

00:33:52.960 --> 00:33:54.240
Some of them

00:33:54.720 --> 00:33:56.440
are nearing the end of their lives,

00:33:57.279 --> 00:33:58.000
but inside,

00:33:59.039 --> 00:34:00.880
they still hold great hope.

00:34:04.200 --> 00:34:05.039
Interesting.

00:34:06.119 --> 00:34:07.240
So, on the streets,

00:34:07.759 --> 00:34:09.119
are those all people carrying hope?

00:34:10.199 --> 00:34:11.599
No, they just got off work.

00:34:13.679 --> 00:34:15.039
Humans just love keeping busy for nothing.